acc_ring - test of GPU direct with OpenACC.
           PGI compiler is required.

$ make
$ mpirun -x PSM2_CUDA=1 -x LD_LIBRARY_PATH -np 8 -npernode 4 ./a.out $((16*1024*1024)) 2>/dev/null
